//! This module provides a development-only WebSocket server that mirrors Tauri commands,
//! allowing Playwright and other browser-based tools to interact with native features.
//!
//! SECURITY:
//! - Only compiled in debug mode (#[cfg(debug_assertions)])
//! - localhost-only binding (127.0.0.1)
//! - Token-based authentication
//! - Command allowlist (no arbitrary execution)

